    "## Pipeline for GridSearchCV\n",
    "We will create a pipeline that includes feature scaling within each iteration of GridSearchCV to ensure that scaling is applied separately within each cross-validation fold. This approach prevents data leakage by ensuring that the scaler is fit only on the training portion of each fold and not on the validation data."
